fields.description:
The classic sample projects (Geocoder and Todo List) default to use SDK 3.5.0.GA despite 3.5.1.GA being installed.

*Steps to reproduce issue*:
1. Install SDK 3.5.0.GA and 3.5.1.GA
2. Create new sample projects of Geocoder and Todo List, classic
3. Notice that the Titanium SDK is set to 3.5.0.GA for both projects

*Expected results*:
Projects are set to use SDK 3.5.1.GA
fields.summary: Geocoder Classic and Todo List Classic projects default to 3.5.0.GA

comments.body: Closing. Very old issue and no longer relivant.
